content: samuveth: Merged two feature-focused PRs this month: #931 adding dynamic watch paths for agent development (+7/-1 lines) and #1571 implementing TEE support for plugin-env (+139/-40 lines). Created two issues that were subsequently closed: #930 requesting hot-reloading for agent dependencies and #893 about running tests on start and dev. Contributed sporadically with activity on just 2 days, focusing equally on feature development and bug fixes across 8 modified files (+150/-45 lines total).
